	<p>The different segments of your accounts may be linked to an organization, an employee or an expense which will facilitate the integration to your general ledger.</p>
	</li>
	<li>
	<span class="fa fa-link"></span>
	<p>Depending on the structure of your organization, our software enables you to link your expenses to a work order, a project or a cost centre. If there are several companies in your corporate group, you may assign expenses incurred, taxes to claim and remit to each company. This will allow you to easily upload the periodic posting in your Accounts Payable.</p>
	</li>
	<li>
	<span class="fa fa-dollar"></span>
