	</li>

	<li>
	<span class="fa fa-database"></span>
	<p>Your data to be imported will include expense amounts, input tax credits (ITC), input tax refunds (ITR) and the temporary recapture of input tax credits (RITC). The detailed posting of expenses may be done both in terms of the employee reimbursements and in terms of credit card payment.</p>
	</li>
